	<div class="component component--section-start" id="30659">
	<div class="component__inner">
			<div class="section-headline">
		<div class="headline">
			<h3 class="headline__headline">Foreign skilled personnel</h3>
	</div>
	</div>
	</div>
</div>
	<div class="component component--container-small" id="30660">
	<div class="component__inner">
			<div class="text-container">
					<h2>Do foreigners have a chance of getting a job in Germany?</h2><p>Skilled job-seekers from abroad have very good opportunities in certain professions. For example, there are many jobs for engineers, doctors, nurses, as well as in the manual trades. Here you can find useful tips and experience reports for international applicants.</p>
			</div>
	</div>
</div>
	
	
